OL,3,CLondon Assembly raises concerns over
OL,4,Ccrowd safety in London
OL,6,FThe London Assembly's Police and Crime
OL,7,FCommittee has published a new report
OL,8,Fscrutinising the Metropolitan Police's
OL,9,Fapproach to public order policing,
OL,10,Fraising concerns about funding
OL,11,Fshortfalls, officer welfare, and
OL,12,Fsafety risks at large-scale events,
OL,13,Fincluding Notting Hill Carnival.
OL,15,FThe report outlines growing pressure
OL,16,Fon the Met Police as it balances a
OL,17,Fsurge in public order operations with
OL,18,Flimited resources and increasing
OL,19,Fstrain on frontline officers.
