OL,3,CLondon Assembly raises concerns over
OL,4,Ccrowd safety in London
OL,6,FAmong the findings, the Committee
OL,7,Fhighlights ongoing concerns about
OL,8,Fcrowd safety at Notting Hill Carnival.
OL,10,FAccording to the report, the Met has
OL,11,Fcontinued to raise the alarm over the
OL,12,Frisk of a potential crush scenario,
OL,13,Fciting high crowd density and
OL,14,Finsufficient stewarding provided by
OL,15,Fevent organisers.
