OL,3,CLondon Assembly raises concerns over
OL,4,Ccrowd safety in London
OL,6,FThe Committee said it shares these
OL,7,Fconcerns and has recommended that the
OL,8,FMayor of London commission a full
OL,9,Freview of crowd density and crowd
OL,10,Fmanagement at the Carnival. The review
OL,11,Fwould inform future stewarding
OL,12,Frequirements and include an assessment
OL,13,Fof known pinch points along the parade
OL,14,Froute.
OL,16,F"The safety of those attending Notting
OL,17,FHill Carnival is paramount, and it is
OL,18,Fclear that more robust crowd
OL,19,Fmanagement planning is needed," the
OL,20,FCommittee states.
