OL,3,CLondon Assembly raises concerns over
OL,4,Ccrowd safety in London
OL,6,FThe report also addresses a number of
OL,7,Fother issues, including policing
OL,8,Ffootball fixtures and protests.
OL,10,FThe Committee also flagged a trend of
OL,11,Ftrained public order officers stepping
OL,12,Fback from these duties, often due to
OL,13,Fthe toll of repeated weekend shifts
OL,14,Fand the impact on their personal lives.
OL,16,FIn addition, the Met's continued
OL,17,Freliance on "abstraction" -
OL,18,Fredeploying neighbourhood officers at
OL,19,Fshort notice to support major public
OL,20,Fevents - is affecting routine policing
OL,21,Fin local communities.
