OL,6,F"Neighbourhood policing teams are
OL,7,Fstretched as officers are regularly
OL,8,Fpulled away to manage central London
OL,9,Fprotests or events. This has an
OL,10,Fongoing impact on public confidence
OL,11,Fand local service delivery," the
OL,12,Freport notes.
OL,14,FThe report makes several
OL,15,Frecommendations to address the
OL,16,Fchallenges facing public order
OL,17,Fpolicing in London, including:
