OL,6,FA Met Police spokesperson said: "The
OL,7,FCommittee's report acknowledges the
OL,8,Funique public order policing demand
OL,9,Fplaced on the Met given the number of
OL,10,Fevents and protests taking place in
OL,11,FLondon.
OL,13,F"Notting Hill Carnival is a key event
OL,14,Fon London's cultural calendar and one
OL,15,Fwhich requires the deployment of a
OL,16,Fvery significant number of officers
OL,17,Fand wider police resources.
