OL,6,F"All those involved in delivering and
OL,7,Fsupporting Carnival are committed to
OL,8,Fensuring it is as safe and secure as
OL,9,Fpossible. We welcomed the recent
OL,10,Fcommissioning of an independent review
OL,11,Fand alongside our partners we are
OL,12,Fconsidering its initial
OL,13,Frecommendations."
